txt.en: 'Have you heard that spies from Gundabad watch Limlók even now?'
Gundabad spies can be found in the Floodfells.\n\nYou should defeat any Gundabad spies that you find.
Sighild, daughter of Runerik and Yrsa, seeks to put an end to the Orc spies skilfully patrolling the Floodfells.

'Oh, I am Sighild. Thyra is my twin sister. Have you heard that spies from Gundabad watch Limlók even now? I can never seem to spot them, but I know they are across the river, skilfully patrolling the Floodfells. We must defeat them to prevent the arrival of more raiding parties.'
